data.meta_description: Open House Saturday July 27 10:00 am to 12:00 pm. Up until 6 months ago this home has been lovingly cared for since it was built in 1965 by the same owners. An addition was added on around 40 years ago creating a large open family room.  There is a large covered deck and tons of storage.  It is close to the hospital and parks.  There is hardwood underneath the carpet in the front room that could be refinished.  The island in the kitchen is unattached and easily moves for convenience.  Listing agent is related to sellers.  Square footage figures are provided as a courtesy estimate only and were obtained from tax data and an estimation of the addition not shown on tax records .  Buyer is advised to obtain an independent measurement.
